Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Finally! We have a connection. No time to explain - you need to learn the basics of a Commandant's responsibility.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Missions from Eden are shown here.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Choose a completed mission.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: You have submitted your post-action report. Now, try swapping a team member's [Memory].

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: [Memory] can be enhanced.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Choose a [Memory] to enhance.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Your team is now ready to continue operations.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Let's try out the new equipment.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: [Memory] provide different bonuses based on the part they are equipped on.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Equip [Memory] of the same name to activate set bonuses.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Wear 2 [Memory] of the same name to activate a set-of-2 bonus.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: We are now ready for battle.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Clear a stage to get equipment as reward.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Let's proceed to the next stage.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Claim your mission reward.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Claim your [Main Quest Mission Reward] from below.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: A new Construct has awakened. Prepare for battle.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Choose your new Construct in [Members].

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Select enough [EXP Materials].

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: We are now ready for battle.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Add the new member to your team.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Increase Construct skill level to increase their prowess in battle.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Choose a Construct from [Members].

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Go to the [Skill] tab.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Choose a [Skill] to upgrade.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Go to the theater of operations.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Liv is currently deployed at the location marked in <color=#00EEEE>[Blue]</color>.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Get a <color=#00EEEE>Blue 3-Ping</color> with another Construct to trigger Liv's [Support Attack].

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: There are many [Novice Mission] that a new Commandant can complete.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Check them out.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: A Construct is available for [Promotion]. Go to the Members page.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Promoting a Construct increases their abilities.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Take note of the promotion requirements.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Try adding another Commandant as your friend.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Try to add a contact.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Tap to switch tabs or view details about a Construct.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: You can play minigames with Constructs in Rendezvous to increase their Affection.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: You can research new [Constructs], [Weapons] and [Memory].

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: I can lend you some [R&D Tickets].

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Don't forget to return them.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Let's try researching.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: A new [Construct] has awakened. Prepare for battle.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Choose your new Construct in [Members].

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Select enough [EXP Materials].

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: We are now ready for battle.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Add your new member and start a battle.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Event mission is now available. Claim your mission reward.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Choose a completed mission.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Daily mission is now available. Claim your mission reward.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Complete daily missions to get [EXP].

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Remember to complete your daily missions!

Name: Celica
Text: Tap here to send a [Support Signal].

Name: Celica
Text: This sends a call for help to nearby squads.

Name: Celica
Text: Let's check out Achievements.

Name: Celica
Text: Claim your achievement rewards here.

Name: Celica
Text: [Targeted Mode] in Research increases the chance of certain equipment appearing.

Name: Celica
Text: Use [Select Equipment] below to set which equipment you want to appear more frequently.

Name: Celica
Text: You can buy supplies in the Shop.

Name: Celica
Text: Training is now ready. Get ready to enter the M.I.N.D.

Name: Celica
Text: Switch to the Daily tab.

Name: Celica
Text: Complete challenges to get [Construct EXP].

Name: Celica
Text: Hello, anybody home? You have a new Dispatch mission.

Name: Celica
Text: Send members on Dispatch missions to earn rewards.

Name: Celica
Text: Oh, I almost forgot! You can change the coating on your Constructs.

Name: Celica
Text: You can find coatings that you own here.

Name: Celica
Text: Hard mode drops lots of [Weapons] and [Consciousness]. It's a good way to obtain and improve your equipment.
Hard mode drops lots of [Weapons] and [Memory]. It's a good way to obtain and improve your equipment.

Name: Celica
Text: Choose Hard Mode.

Name: Celica
Text: Get Construct Shards to activate [Evolve].

Name: Celica
Text: Tap [Activate].

Name: Celica
Text: We are now ready for battle.

Name: Celica
Text: You can use your record from the previous battle to simulate results in Auto Clear.

Name: Celica
Text: This feature becomes available once you have cleared a stage, reducing your workload.

Name: Celica
Text: Let's recycle some resources!

Name: Celica
Text: Switch to the Daily tab.

Name: Celica
Text: As you level up, so will your Challenges, as well as the rewards.

Name: Celica
Text: Bounty Missions are now available!

Name: Celica
Text: You can see Bounty Missions here.

Name: Celica
Text: Let's go to the Cog collection battlefield.

Name: Celica
Text: Switch to the Daily tab.

Name: Celica
Text: As you level up, so will your Challenges, as well as the rewards.

Name: Celica
Text: View Construct details here.

Name: Celica
Text: Continue the operation.

Name: Celica
Text: Choose Stronghold mode.

Name: Celica
Text: Complete Stronghold battles to increase [Dispatch Income].

Name: Celica
Text: Phantom Pain Cage is now available. Are you ready?

Name: Celica
Text: Switch to the Challenge tab.

Name: Celica
Text: Defeat the boss to get [Currency] that can be exchanged for resources.

Name: Celica
Text: We are now ready for battle.

Name: Celica
Text: Check it out if you want to know more about Constructs.

Name: Celica
Text: We are now ready for battle.

Name: Celica
Text: Challenges have a chance to drop Construct Shards.

Name: Celica
Text: Memory Rescue is now available.

Name: Celica
Text: Switch to the Challenge tab.

Name: Celica
Text: Complete quests and earn [Equipment].

Name: Celica
Text: Go to the War Zone now!

Name: Celica
Text: Switch to the Challenge tab.

Name: Celica
Text: Complete Challenges to get [Black Cards].

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: Let's equip the gear that you just obtained.

Name: Mysterious Girl
Text: [EXP] spent on the previous equipment is fully-refunded when you change equipment.

Name: Celica
Text: Go to [Overclock].

Name: Celica
Text: Switch to the Daily tab.

Name: Celica
Text: Overclock resets equipment level, but greatly increases their attribute growth.

Name: Celica
Text: Go to [Operation EXEM].

Name: Celica
Text: Switch to the Daily tab.

Name: Celica
Text: There is a chance to get [High-Rank Equipment] from Challenges.
